<dl id="n10105j"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n10" href="#n10105j">N10 (VI.B.16)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n10all.htm#n10105j"> 105(j)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> slap in the face</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">An unintelligible word or two might be condoned, but to have everything I had essayed to convey to my listeners fall upon Maggie&apos;s ears as any possible language foreign to her learning &mdash; that was like a <mark>slap in the face</mark>, and far more humiliating. <small> Pierre V.R. Key, Louis. <a name="PVRK" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#PVRK"><cite title="source">John McCormack: His own life story</cite></a> (1918) 37</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
